                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <head>No. 86.<lb/>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Davis</persName>
                            to Mr. <persName type="to">Reinberg</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Department
                                    of State</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1885-01-17">
                            <hi rend="italic">January</hi> 17,
                            1885</date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Santos naturalized July 6, ʹ74. Department has record. Will send copy. Inform
                        Government and request release.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>DAVIS.</signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
